This paper deals with energy efficiency optimization in wireless communication systems, which involves information theory, networking, and system optimization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
